            "text": "A small kitchen, a short menu, an honest room.",
            "size": "6xl"
          }
        },
        "text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We opened Saffron in 2023 to cook the way we eat at home — slowly, seasonally, and with whoever we have at the table.</p>",
