        "left-heading": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "We cook around the market.",
            "size": "3xl",
            "position": "left"
          }
        },
        "right-text-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Mondays are spent reading the week — what's landing at the market, what's worth buying, what's worth waiting another week for. The menu is written on Tuesday morning and printed Tuesday afternoon.</p>",
            "size": "base",
            "uppercase": false,
            "muted": false,
            "position": "right"
          }
        },
        "right-text-2": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Our suppliers are mostly people, not companies. A grower in the Hudson Valley, a fisherman off Montauk, a butcher in Red Hook. The room is small enough that we can cook for it carefully.</p>",
            "size": "base",
            "uppercase": false,
            "muted": false,
            "position": "right"
          }
        },
